OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1774901153
OL,3,CUK government must do more for Brits
OL,4,Cdetained in UAE, says campaign group
OL,6,FA UK-based campaign group has called
OL,7,Fon the government to help Brits
OL,8,Fcurrently detained in the UAE over
OL,9,Fstrict cybercrime laws, expressing its
OL,10,Fconcerns for their well-being, ITV
OL,11,FNews understands.
OL,13,FRadha Stirling, CEO of Detained in
OL,14,FDubai, has said that it is
OL,15,F"disgraceful" that more is not being
OL,16,Fdone to help those who have been
OL,17,Fcharged under the United Arab
OL,18,FEmirates' (UAE) cybercrime laws in
OL,19,Fconnection with videos and social
OL,20,Fmedia posts about recent Iranian drone
OL,21,Fand missile strikes.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
