OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1774901153
OL,3,CUK government must do more for Brits
OL,4,Cdetained in UAE, says campaign group
OL,6,FIt is unclear exactly how many Brits
OL,7,Fare currently detained in Dubai. The
OL,8,FForeign Office has confirmed at least
OL,9,Ffive individuals are receiving
OL,10,Fconsular assistance, while others have
OL,11,Falready been released.
OL,13,FThere is no obligation for British
OL,14,Fnationals to inform the FCDO that they
OL,15,Fare detained.
OL,17,FStirling warns there may be as many as
OL,18,F70 active cases, adding that some
OL,19,Fdetainees are not going to the embassy
OL,20,Ffor help as they "don't feel
OL,21,Fconfident" in the Foreign Office.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
