OL,3,CUK government must do more for Brits
OL,4,Cdetained in UAE, says campaign group
OL,6,FEarlier this month, the British
OL,7,FEmbassy in the UAE strongly advised
OL,8,FBritons against taking pictures or
OL,9,Fsharing images of missile impact.
OL,11,FThe UAE's Attorney-General warned that
OL,12,Fthose in Dubai who post images and
OL,13,Fvideo online of "incident sites or
OL,14,Fdamage" caused by missiles will face
OL,15,Flegal action "without leniency".
OL,17,FDetained in Dubai say that individuals
OL,18,Fare being detained for taking photos
OL,19,For videos, even in cases where the
OL,20,Fmaterial was "not shared or published".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
