OL,3,CUK government must do more for Brits
OL,4,Cdetained in UAE, says campaign group
OL,6,F"What began as public warnings", they
OL,7,Fsay, "rapidly escalated into
OL,8,Fwidespread arrests, detention, and
OL,9,Fprosecution of residents, tourists,
OL,10,Fworkers, and students of multiple
OL,11,Fnationalities".
OL,13,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,14,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,15,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,16,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
