CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1774901153
OL,3,CUK government must do more for Brits
OL,4,Cdetained in UAE, says campaign group
OL,6,FDetained in Dubai, who are supporting
OL,7,Fseveral detainees in the UAE, and
OL,8,Ftheir families, claim they are
OL,9,F"desperate" and concerned that their
OL,10,Floved ones are "suffering".
OL,12,FThe group also cites accounts from
OL,13,Fcurrent detainees, claiming they are
OL,14,Fstaying in overcrowded cells, have
OL,15,Flimited access to food, a lack of
OL,16,Fmedical care, restricted communication.
OL,18,FA representative for the government of
OL,19,FDubai media office did not immediately
OL,20,Frespond to ITV News' request for
OL,21,Fcomment.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
