OL,3,CUK government must do more for Brits
OL,4,Cdetained in UAE, says campaign group
OL,6,FAn FCDO spokesperson said: "We are
OL,7,Fproviding consular assistance to a
OL,8,Fsmall number of British nationals
OL,9,Fdetained in the UAE in connection with
OL,10,Fthis issue, and our Ambassador is
OL,11,Fengaging with the Emirati authorities
OL,12,Fabout their cases."
OL,14,FThe FCDO add that British nationals
OL,15,Fcan contact the FCDO on +44 20 7008
OL,16,F5000 to request support.
OL,18,FFrom Westminster to Washington DC -
OL,19,Four political experts are across all
OL,20,Fthe latest key talking points. Listen
OL,21,Fto the latest episode below...
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/8
